OL,5, A law firm has launched an             
OL,6, investigation after allegations senior 
OL,7, members of staff treated a Cardiff     
OL,8, restaurant manager badly.              
OL,10,FLily Griffiths, 22, had served the     
OL,11,Fgroup of six at Cora, Pontcanna, where 
OL,12,Fthey spent #1,000.                     
OL,14,FOwner Lee Skeet called it his "biggest 
OL,15,Fbill ever" - but gave the money to Ms  
OL,16,FGriffiths, saying what happened to her 
OL,17,F"broke my heart".                      
OL,19,FLaw firm Ince said it was aware of     
OL,20,Fallegations and was investigating.     
